Title: Biography: Johnny Depp

reviewText: The presentation was made in 2004 so as of this review it is a decade or so old. This means that the history is relevant but the future is missing. We also probably have a revised history as more information comes to light.It is in sound bite form so we have sever people repeatedly making one or two liners without following through with the thought before someone else speaks.This may be abbreviated form a longer presentation. However the essence of the presentation is included in this 50 minute program.I had forgotten about some of the films Johnny Depp made so this was a good refresher.
summary: A tad dated - yet a fair amount of information in sound bite form.
Title: Biography: Johnny Depp

reviewText: If you're a fan like me, then the idea of owning Johnny Depps biography is a thrilling one. But wait, because June 27, 2006 A&E; will be rereleasing this film onto DVD for under twenty dollars.I for one, am greatly excited!
Title: Biography: Johnny Depp

reviewText: I can't tell if he's being honest or acting the part of who he thinks he is supposed to be.  Still, it's Johnny Depp, and whether the personality is true or made up, he's still cute as a button.
